## What's Changed
* Add support for Amphp Postgres by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/database-test-case/pull/9
* Add support for MySQL in PdoConnectionAdapter by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/database-test-case/pull/10
* Update supported connection types by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/database-test-case/pull/11


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/database-test-case/compare/0.1.0...0.2.0
